%h2 Organisational Control Page - Add New Activity
- form_for :activity, :url => { :action => 'create'} do |f|
  = render :partial => 'contact', :locals => { :f => f }
  %p
    Click 'Create' to add the Activity. You will be taken back to the Activities page where you can then send an access key to the newly-created Activity Manager.
  #activity_creator{:style => @activity_creator.nil? ? 'display:none' : 'display:block'} 
    %p
      Alternatively, you can send this link to anyone to allow them to create activities inside your organisation:
      %br
      = text_field_tag 'activity_creator_url', @activity_creator_url, :onclick => 'this.select()', :style => 'width:450px'
  #activity_link_creator{:style => @activity_creator.nil? ? 'display:block' : 'display:none'} 
    %p
      If you wish to create a link, which other people can follow to create activities within your organisation, please click
      %span#here_link
        =link_to_remote 'here.', :url => {:action => 'generate_activity_creator', :controller => 'activities'}, :update => 'activity_link', :complete => "$('activity_link_creator').hide(); $('activity_creator').show()"
  %span.button
    = submit_tag "Create", :disable_with => 'Creating...'
%span.button
  = link_to 'Back', :action => :incomplete
